			<h4 class="con_in_tit04">Greetings from the President</h4>
			<p class="con_in_txt">I have been working as a gastroenterologist at a university for more than 40 years, and my dream was to build a hospital brings wellness to patients as well as those who are healthy. In 2008, the Vievis Namuh Hospital was established to become a hospital that can diagnose diseases and provide all the care necessary for our customers to become healthy. </p>

			<p class="con_in_txt">As Korea's first and best to specialize in gastrointestinal diseases, Vievis Namuh Hospital strives to offer the best solution for individual situation and characteristics, including health screenings, outpatient treatments, and surgeries. </p>

			<p class="con_in_txt">We are equipped with state-of-the-art diagnostic equipment at the level of to university hospitals, and all of our specialists consist of doctors who have served as professors at university hospitals. We have improved the quality of medical services by having all of our specialists in gastroenterology obtain the license as gastrointestinal endoscopy specialists. </p>

			<p class="con_in_txt">In addition to improving the quality of treatment, we have enhanced the convenience through a one-stop system that allows both examination and result consultation on the day of treatment. We are also taking charge to organize programs that accommodate our customers by developing a colonoscopy process that does not require patients to take laxatives.Vievi-Namuh Hospital will always do our best to promote everyone's digestive health. </p>
